## 📋 Week 5 구현 명령어 (8개)

### 1️⃣ AND (0x20) - 논리곱

```rust
fn exec_and(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    // Pop two values
    let b = self.pop()?;  // Second operand (top)
    let a = self.pop()?;  // First operand

    // Bitwise AND
    let result = a & b;

    // Push result
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [a, b, ...]
After:  [a & b, ...]
```

---

### 2️⃣ OR (0x21) - 논리합

```rust
fn exec_or(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let b = self.pop()?;
    let a = self.pop()?;

    let result = a | b;
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [a, b, ...]
After:  [a | b, ...]
```

---

### 3️⃣ NOT (0x22) - 논리부정

```rust
fn exec_not(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let a = self.pop()?;

    // Bitwise NOT
    let result = !a;
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [a, ...]
After:  [~a, ...]
```

---

### 4️⃣ XOR (0x23) - 배타적논리합

```rust
fn exec_xor(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let b = self.pop()?;
    let a = self.pop()?;

    let result = a ^ b;
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

---

### 5️⃣ EQ (0x24) - 같음 (==)

```rust
fn exec_eq(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let b = self.pop()?;
    let a = self.pop()?;

    // Compare equality: 1 if equal, 0 if not
    let result = if a == b { 1 } else { 0 };
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [a, b, ...]
After:  [1 or 0, ...]  (1 if a==b, 0 otherwise)
```

---

### 6️⃣ NEQ (0x25) - 다름 (!=)

```rust
fn exec_neq(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let b = self.pop()?;
    let a = self.pop()?;

    // Compare inequality: 1 if not equal, 0 if equal
    let result = if a != b { 1 } else { 0 };
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

---

### 7️⃣ LT (0x26) - 작음 (<)

```rust
fn exec_lt(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let b = self.pop()?;  // Right operand
    let a = self.pop()?;  // Left operand

    // Signed comparison
    let a_i64 = a as i64;
    let b_i64 = b as i64;
    let result = if a_i64 < b_i64 { 1 } else { 0 };
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [a, b, ...]
After:  [1 or 0, ...]  (1 if a<b, 0 otherwise)
```

---

### 8️⃣ LTE (0x27) - 작거나같음 (<=)

```rust
fn exec_lte(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    let b = self.pop()?;
    let a = self.pop()?;

    // Signed comparison
    let a_i64 = a as i64;
    let b_i64 = b as i64;
    let result = if a_i64 <= b_i64 { 1 } else { 0 };
    self.push(result)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

